      <title>俄罗斯法院取消扣押摩根大通银行与俄罗斯外贸银行争议中的部分资金</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/russian-court-cancels-seizure-part-jpmorgan-banks-funds-dispute-with-russias-vtb-2024-05-02/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一份法庭文件显示，俄罗斯一家法院在与俄罗斯国有银行 VTB 的纠纷中取消了对摩根大通在俄罗斯的部分资金的扣押。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/russian-court-cancels-seizure-part-jpmorgan-banks-funds-dispute-with-russias-vtb-2024-05-02/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 06:32:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国合作银行表示合并谈判“进展顺利”，重组即将完成</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/britains-co-op-bank-says-merger-talks-well-advanced-revamp-almost-complete-2024-05-02/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国合作银行周四表示，考文垂建筑协会收购该银行的谈判“进展顺利”，在报告第一季度财务业绩符合预期后，其多年的改革现已基本完成。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/britains-co-op-bank-says-merger-talks-well-advanced-revamp-almost-complete-2024-05-02/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 06:30:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Raiffeisen 表示 Strabag 交易正在经过仔细的风险评估</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/raiffeisen-says-strabag-deal-under-careful-risk-assessment-2024-05-02/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯最大的西方银行雷夫艾森国际银行 (RBI) 周四表示，该银行仍在仔细评估收购与一位俄罗斯大亨有关的建筑公司 Strabag 的股份是否存在合规风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/raiffeisen-says-strabag-deal-under-careful-risk-assessment-2024-05-02/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 05:51:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>ING 宣布股票回购，季度净利息收入下降</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/ing-posts-lower-q1-net-interest-income-higher-interest-rates-lift-funding-costs-2024-05-02/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[ING Groep 周四宣布回购 25 亿欧元的股票，此前这家荷兰银行表示，尽管净利息收入（一项关键盈利指标）下降，但高利率推动第一季度业绩强劲。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/ing-posts-lower-q1-net-interest-income-higher-interest-rates-lift-funding-costs-2024-05-02/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 05:14:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>《朝鲜日报》称瑞士信贷可能因卖空韩国而面临 3600 万美元的罚款</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/credit-suisse-may-face-36-mln-fine-over-skorea-short-selling-says-chosun-ilbo-2024-05-02/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国《朝鲜日报》周四援引业内消息人士的话称，韩国金融当局已通知瑞士信贷银行，该公司可能因涉嫌违反卖空规则而面临 500 亿韩元（3632 万美元）的罚款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/credit-suisse-may-face-36-mln-fine-over-skorea-short-selling-says-chosun-ilbo-2024-05-02/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 04:42:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>汇丰维持香港最优惠贷款利率于5.875%不变</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hsbc-keeps-best-lending-rate-hong-kong-unchanged-5875-2024-05-02/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[汇丰控股周四表示，在香港事实上的央行维持通过隔夜贴现窗口收取的基本利率不变，追随美联储维持利率稳定的决定后，该公司已将香港最优惠贷款利率维持在5.875%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hsbc-keeps-best-lending-rate-hong-kong-unchanged-5875-2024-05-02/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 04:27:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>渣打银行利润超过收入增长预期</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/standard-chartered-q1-profit-rises-55-beats-estimates-2024-05-02/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[渣打银行周四第一季度税前利润超出预期，增长 5.5%，原因是利率上升带来的收入增加以及市场交易业务的强劲表现抵消了信贷损失的激增。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/standard-chartered-q1-profit-rises-55-beats-estimates-2024-05-02/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 04:24:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>香港央行维持关键利率不变，追踪美联储决定</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/hong-kong-central-bank-keeps-key-rate-unchanged-tracks-fed-move-2024-05-02/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港金融管理局（金管局）周四将通过隔夜贴现窗口收取的基本利率维持在 5.75% 不变，以追随美联储维持利率稳定的决定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/hong-kong-central-bank-keeps-key-rate-unchanged-tracks-fed-move-2024-05-02/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 03:21:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>星展银行季度业绩超出预期，有望再创纪录</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/singapore-bank-dbs-first-quarter-net-profit-rises-15-year-record-high-2024-05-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新加坡最大的银行星展集团周四公布第一季度业绩，全面增长超出预期，并表示预计净利润将超过去年创纪录的业绩。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/singapore-bank-dbs-first-quarter-net-profit-rises-15-year-record-high-2024-05-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 22:39:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
